286
00:18:01.714 --> 00:18:02.714
Mmm.

287
00:18:03.616 --> 00:18:04.845
[Cliff sighs] Fuck me.

288
00:18:05.518 --> 00:18:08.044
[Larry] Sometimes it helps to
picture a place you'd like to go.

289
00:18:08.854 --> 00:18:10.454
