I can't feel! I can't eat.

293
00:18:20.399 --> 00:18:23.096
I can't smell. can't
shit. I can't fuck

294
00:18:23.235 --> 00:18:25.380
and I'd like to be able to do
one fucking thing for myself

295
00:18:25.404 --> 00:18:27.316
when I kiss you and the
other fucking Munster here

296
