326
00:19:50.189 --> 00:19:52.351
[Mr. Morden] <i>Lovely Rita.</i>

327
00:19:52.458 --> 00:19:53.949
<i>Queen of '50s cinema.</i>

328
00:19:54.026 --> 00:19:56.655
