398
00:24:57.830 --> 00:24:59.264
Yeah!

399
00:25:03.002 --> 00:25:04.129
Yeah!

400
00:25:25.657 --> 00:25:28.559
My family thinks I died in a
car crash seven years ago.

401
00:25:29.661 --> 00:25:31.581
My daughter's probably
grown up without a father.

402
00:25:32.464 --> 00:25:33.830
