for you. that you're walking.

409
00:25:52.418 --> 00:25:54.182
that you finally feel like you.

410
00:25:55.921 --> 00:25:58.720
All I wanted was to give
you a gentle place to land.

411
00:25:59.691 --> 00:26:01.182
A second chance.

412
00:26:02.061 --> 00:26:03.495
And I appreciate that.

413
00:26:12.504 --> 00:26:14.496
