been altering your memories

417
00:26:25.184 --> 00:26:26.447
to help you cope.

418
00:26:39.731 --> 00:26:41.700
[Cliff on tape] <i>I don't
know what happened to us.</i>

419
00:26:43.035 --> 00:26:44.526
<i>I'm going to be better.</i>

420
00:26:44.903 --> 00:26:45.903
