433
00:28:13.759 --> 00:28:15.660
I don't know what
happened to us.

434
00:28:18.497 --> 00:28:19.988
I'm going to be better.

435
00:28:21.333 --> 00:28:23.632
- I know it's late.
- [Kate] <i>Hello?</i>

436
00:28:23.802 --> 00:28:24.802
Hey.

437
00:28:28.073 --> 00:28:29.073
