443
00:29:18.857 --> 00:29:19.950
[tires screeching]

444
00:29:21.927 --> 00:29:22.967
[indistinct radio chatter]

445
00:29:24.429 --> 00:29:25.522
You're okay.

446
00:29:25.764 --> 00:29:27.562
[Cliff] No. Kate!

447
00:29:29.401 --> 00:29:30.869
Oh. God. No.

448
00:29:31.737 --> 00:29:34.229
Clara. What happened to Clara?

449
