I'm afraid you were
the only survivor.

450
00:29:40.612 --> 00:29:43.707
[Cliff] No! No. no!

451
00:29:46.418 --> 00:29:47.716
No. no!

452
00:29:48.086 --> 00:29:50.419
No. no. no!

453
00:29:50.555 --> 00:29:52.217
No!

454
00:30:09.941 --> 00:30:11.273
I can't feel pain.

455
00:30:12.010 --> 00:30:13.535
